```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Extension
    participant Server as Server<br/>127.0.0.1:4597
    participant Provider as Email Provider<br/>OAuth Server
    participant DB as Database
    
    User->>Extension: Click "Add Account"
    Extension->>Server: GET /auth/{provider}/start
    Server->>DB: Create OAuth state
    Server-->>Extension: Redirect URL
    
    Extension->>Provider: Redirect to OAuth
    Provider-->>User: Login Prompt
    User->>Provider: Enter credentials
    Provider-->>Extension: Auth code
    
    Extension->>Server: POST /auth/{provider}/callback
    Server->>Provider: Exchange code for tokens
    Provider-->>Server: Access + Refresh tokens
    
    Server->>DB: Store encrypted tokens
    Server-->>Extension: Success
    
    Note over Extension,DB: Future: Auto-refresh tokens before expiry
```